// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2400 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 765f5c15-97e1-50e9-bf8d-f25781270131

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
